2026-04-22 21:30:24,209 - openai._base_client - DEBUG - Request options: {'method': 'post', 'url': '/chat/completions', 'files': None, 'json_data': {'messages': [{'role': 'user', 'content': "You are an expert movie subtitle translator.\nCRITICAL INSTRUCTIONS:\n1. Target Language: Vietnamese. You MUST translate EXACTLY into this language. Do not leave lines in the original language.\n2. Completeness: You MUST translate every single line. I am providing EXACTLY 115 lines. The output MUST contain EXACTLY 115 lines. Do NOT skip, drop, merge, or split any lines. All IDs from 1 to 115 MUST be present in the output.\n3. Format: You MUST strictly use the format: ID|Translated_Text\n4. Output Only: Provide ONLY the translated lines. No explanations, no introductory text, no extra spaces.\n5. Context: Keep the meaning and tone natural, and maintain context between consecutive lines.\n\n\nTranslate the following subtitle content into Vietnamese:\n\n<subtitles>\n1|(Good Fortune)\n2|(happy New Year)\n3|(Shen Mengtang President, Huanyu Group)\n4|the fact that I could so smoothly\n5|take over from my father\n6|huanyu Real Estate,\n7|is all thanks\n8|to the incredible support from all of you.\n9|I've decided\n10|I've decided\n11|that every employee's year-end bonus\n12|gets an extra 20,000.\n13|You corrupt merchant!\n14|(Zhang Da Son of Zhang Father)\n15|you killed my father!\n16|(Lu Chuan Shen Mengtang's Secretary)\n17|president Shen.\n18|Those are\n19|Haicheng\n20|construction team uniforms.\n21|If he'd only been paid,\n22|my dad\n23|could've had New Year's\n24|with his grandson.\n25|You have money\n26|to throw such a lavish annual party,\n27|but you wouldn't give\n28|my dad\n29|an 8,000 wage?\n30|Nonsense!\n31|Huanyu always pays on time.\n32|Each year,\n33|we set aside 300 million\n34|as a fund\n35|of paying all\n36|their wages.\n37|(Zhang Father Zhang Da's Father)\n38|then why\n39|why did he\n40|jump to his death\n41|over an 8,000 wage?\n42|President Shen,\n43|the year-end bonus she gives us\n44|is more than 8,000.\n45|How could she withhold\n46|workers' wages?\n47|We know her character.\n48|Who here doesn't?\n49|Your dad must have\n50|drank too much and fell.\n51|You're using your dad's death\n52|to extort money!\n53|That's impossible.\n54|It must be fake.\n55|I'm telling the truth!\n56|I'm telling the truth.\n57|Why don't you believe me?\n58|Ah!\n59|You don't believe me?\n60|Ah!\n61|You don't believe me?\n62|(Pesticide)\n63|president Shen!\n64|He's going to poison himself!\n65|Don't!\n66|Don't drink!\n67|I believe you.\n68|Let's just talk this out.\n69|You\n70|you\n71|You do?\n72|Yes.\n73|I do.\n74|No.\n75|You're lying to me!\n76|You're the president of Huanyu Group.\n77|My dad\n78|You drove him to his death!\n79|Today,\n80|I'm going to\n81|ruin your reputation!\n82|You big shots,\n83|you have no idea\n84|our suffering.\n85|At the bottom.\n86|Go to the Haicheng site\n87|and see.\n88|Huh?\n89|How many workers' wages\n90|haven't been paid?\n91|Could it be\n92|Was I deceived?\n93|(One day later)\n94|Miss Shen,\n95|are you sure\n96|pose as a safety officer\n97|undercover at the Haicheng site?\n98|The Haicheng team's books\n99|show no issues.\n100|(Financial Report)\n101|but a worker is dead.\n102|I have to investigate this.\n103|But staying at the site alone\n104|is just too dangerous.\n105|I have to go undercover myself\n106|to find out\n107|if any workers are being underpaid.\n108|If they are,\n109|I need to see\n110|who exactly is deceiving me\n111|and embezzling their hard-earned money.\n112|(Haicheng Huanyu Group)\n113|(Gao Weimin Haicheng Worker)\n114|my leg!\n115|My leg!\n</subtitles>"}], 'model': 'translategemma:12b'}}
